Package com.liliya.quiz.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Player
    Represents a player who is launching and playing quizzes
    PlayerQuizInstance
    Player Quiz Instance represents every instance of a quiz played by a player It reflects the many to many relationship between players and quizzes Each instance is denoted by its total score and whether the player is actively playing or not
    Question
    Question as part of hte questions in a quiz
    Quiz
    A class used to create new quiz objects The objects will contain the list of questions for each quiz game set up on the server
    QuizService
    The server functionality of the quiz system
